{"title":"融雪","authors":["赵丽宏"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":4,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"融雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵丽宏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赴京出席七届全国政协会议，欣逢一夜春雪，浮想联翩，感而赋之。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"降落在无声的夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天冷雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是黑暗中的发泄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒来但见艳阳灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一束阳光都在喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融雪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长安街上融雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车流未断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人潮激越"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几道潮湿的车辙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转瞬便化为轻烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前融雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场坦荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碑石莹洁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几滩平静的水渍里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮云如翱翔的白鸽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风筝如飘舞的满月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒冬气数已尽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间再难容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即便曾一度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺天盖地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终究要让位于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请听融雪有声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声如雨洒平湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声如蚕噬桑叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声如泉出幽谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声如江河奔泻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有声的融雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细微却恢宏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柔弱却壮烈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会屈服于雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融雪声中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿叶已吐芽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花蕾正萌结"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪的融化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报告着春的大捷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是冬的尾声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是春的序言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然阳光无法垄断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不再害怕落雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪落了也要化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不化的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望春天的血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不冷却的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春血液呵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1988.3.25．北京。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}